    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-04-16T18:50:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-04-16T09:51:00-05:00" n="1099"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1099">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Woodford</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1898-04-16T23:59:59+00:09"
                            notBefore="1898-04-16T15:00:00+00:09" when="1898-04-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 16, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Informed this morning (Saturday) by the United States consul at Malaga that his
                    consulate was mobbed last night. I immediately demanded protection by Spanish
                    Government of all American consulates in Spain. Local Spanish authorities at
                    Malaga have suppressed the mob and replaced the United States shield, which had
                    been destroyed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1898-04-16T23:59:59+00:09"
                            notBefore="1898-04-16T15:00:00+00:09" when="1898-04-16">Saturday
                            Evening</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodford.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
